<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُ الآخَر في صَاحِبٍ لَهُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>رَبَّنَا إِنَّ هَذَا * وَاحِدُ النَّاسِ حَقَّا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَرِفْقَاً يَا رَبَّنَا * بِالقَوَارِيرِ رِفْقَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَعَمْرِي مَا أَنْزَلَ * رَبُّكَ بِكَ رِقَّا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إِلاَّ لِيُجَدِّدَا * بَعْدَهُ لَكَ العِتْقَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَتَرَى فَضْلَ اللهِ * وَيَرَى اللهُ الصِّدْقَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عُوفِيتَ فَمِثْلُكَ * أَحَقُّ بِأَنْ يَبْقَى<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>